<bibRefCitation id="A7215020DAF1B080676F5413451425EF" author="Sugonjaev, ES" journalOrPublisher="Entomologicheskoe Obozrenie" pageId="21" pageNumber="70" pagination="417 - 425" title="Chalcid wasps (Hymenoptera, Chalcidoidea) parasites of soft scales (Coccinea, Coccidae) in Vietnam. IV. New species of the genus Microterys Thomson and Metaphycus Mercet (Encyrtidae), partly inhabiting ants' nests, with morphological notes." volume="75" year="1996">Sugonjaev 1996</bibRefCitation>
